text: Paul Kölliker (19 February 193211 January 2021) was a Swiss rower. He competed in the men's coxless four event at the 1960 Summer Olympics. He was born in Wolfwil, Switzerland. Kölliker died on 11 January 2021 at the age of 88. ==References== Category:1932 births Category:2021 deaths Category:Olympians for Switzerland Category:Rowers
